common.model

Class FrequencyList

  • java.lang.Object
    • common.model.FrequencyList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICopy, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<Frequency>

    public class FrequencyList
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<Frequency>, ICopy, java.io.Serializable
    Stores and manages a number of frequency objects. Ensures that frequencies always add to MAX_FREQ (i.e 100). Automatically adjusts Frequencies and priorities.
    Author:
    Nicholas Panzarino, jasirocki - jdoc
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
